    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "Maybe allowing the users to define custom methods to be called on specific actions on the widget. They could either override the default behavior of our widgets or plug themselves into the flow. \n\nOr maybe this could simply be handled with emitting global events and letting the user listen to the `on:refine` and change the url from here.\n",
