    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "I'm not fond of the third solution (option on the widget). It will clutter the API in the end, we can't handle all use-cases.\n\nI don't think I'm familiar with the refine hook, how does it work?\n\nI like the refine event on the widget idea. A global refine event could work as well if we can have access to the originating widget from the event itself (`event.from` being the widget instance?)\n",
