  {
    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "Refine hook should cut it, always tricky to provide events that in the end are disabling a behavior. The dom handle this by passing event and event.preventDefault but that would look like weird in our case I guess.\n\nSo passing a refineHook(value, refine) where you need to call refine, would allow good crazy implementations and use cases.\n\nWorks?\n",
